  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess the influence of the severity of chronic periodontitis on
      hemodynamic parameters in hypertensive patients.Secondary purposes of this protocol is to
      identify evolution of several biomarkers and correlate the clinical situation with oral
      microflora.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
